# TradingFlow Frontend Rules

- Keep UI minimal using shadcn primitives and Tailwind utilities.
- Prefer readable React patterns: early returns, small components, clear state names.
- For protected screens, enforce auth gating and redirect unauthenticated users to `/auth`.
- For unstable or heavy modules (workflow builder/editor), use lazy route loading to avoid blank app startup.
- Surface backend errors clearly in forms and page states.
- After changes, verify page load for `/`, `/auth`, and any touched routes.
